title: B.A.A.S Musubi
description:
Ono New Twist on a Spam Musubi!

Ingredients: 
- 1/2 can of Spam
- 1 cup cooked white rice, seasoned with furikake and toasted sesame seeds
- 5 whole sheet nori
- 6 strips of bacon
- 1/2 cup mayo
- 3 tablespoons ichimi (chili) powder
- 4 tablespoon sesame oil
- 1/2 lb ahi steak
- 1/2 avocado (sliced)

Directions:
1. Cut ahi into cubes
2. Add t tablespoons sesame oil and mix to coat fish.
3. In large skillet, cook SPAM Classic and bacon until lightly brown and crisp.
4. Place nori into musubi maker. Place SPAM on nori; add in spicy ahi, bacon strip and avocado slices on top of spam. Top with rice; press down. Remove SPAM and rice from musubi press.
5. On work surface, lay nori shiny-side-down; top with SPAM mixture. Wrap up. Cut each musubi in half. Slice each half diagonally into 2 pieces. Serve immediately.
